{"tid":413511,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"周秀娜性感出海 皮包骨嚇親網民","createTime":"2017-09-25T13:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T04:07:16.000Z","uid":14730,"like":10,"dislike":152,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5ebec82bf55b770fdd31394557cc1d3a9d9507cb","tid":413511,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/211015_7dfadf37a0824cb4dc16b643a89688b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F211015_7dfadf37a0824cb4dc16b643a89688b3.jpg&h=189efd29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n32歲周秀娜身形愈來愈瘦，無復昔日豐滿體態。昨日她在社交網站上載穿著粉紅色衫、白色短褲，露肩又騷腰，與友人出海釣魚，開心拍照展示成果。不過，娜姐體形瘦削，褲頭都鬆鬆的。不少網民留言說被她嚇親，指她實在太瘦，似皮包骨有點恐怖，叫她吃多些增肥。亦有網民留意她有腹肌，相信是練拳的成績，說欣賞她，最重要健康。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2htuVDv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2htuVDv&d=XPJFyjIw5KXs1tGco9R6fMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2b7f7037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2htuVDv</a>"},{"pid":"0272a17a3642f499f8f0a7efeafc68e53e7ef6fb","tid":413511,"uid":2545,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"除左副超呢個樣應該嚇撚死人"},{"pid":"16fa2cbe12bb27757529c3e5fe4e7929b810ea64","tid":413511,"uid":10014,"like":60,"dislike":16,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"個樣其實好正<br />\n<br />\n只係拆左彈後無晒吸引力<br />\n<br />\n好想食潮州妹"},{"pid":"e2870d27063c9db75c5ab66f53f74c3f73386201","tid":413511,"uid":88006,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"睇錯下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c080f0d92cf2726708a2e33082b5957203df6b8d","tid":413511,"uid":132447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"係咪有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa264554b26deafda03bca4b4fe8bda267a786